{"tid":56331,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝修撚] 想撕牆紙上油應該點搞","createTime":"2016-12-27T07:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T16:44:34.000Z","uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d507dde8709819744cb6587f46b121d4128e6c","tid":56331,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:09:54.000Z","msg":"唔知應該開咩台,開錯唔好意思先<br />\n<br />\n是咁的,呢排好得閒,想搵啲野搞下<br />\n<br />\n咁間房都殘殘地就諗不如裝潢下啦<br />\n<br />\n間房就用緊牆紙,想話撕左佢再油油,但想問問係咪撕左牆紙之後唔係即刻上油,要扇灰?<br />\n<br />\n無咩呢方面經驗所以想問問各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941a2ffbcfd9908de2ffbf6a70a33cd9f17abcbf","tid":56331,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"唔撕就咁上效果都ok 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b82a604ccc890646b339b2305b4cfc7b80034f","tid":56331,"uid":69269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撕就咁上效果都ok 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但過多排甩牆紙又係要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a5d15ba6e54b1635bd43cc93e4d2a645bdf1a8","tid":56331,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"屋企呢啲硬件就應該開去硬件台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常嚟講撕完牆紙要再批灰，減少牆身凹凸不平<br />\n上油正常又要加些少天拿水去開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔識嘅話都係搵師傅做啦"},{"pid":"afac46d3bc70fb4bac83b66bf904e35b7a824dec","tid":56331,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"自己油 預左一定唔靚喎"},{"pid":"e563720d0700339ecc87ee62fba1f6bc3111d4cc","tid":56331,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企呢啲硬件就應該開去硬件台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常嚟講撕完牆紙要再批灰，減少牆身凹凸不平<br />\n上油正常又要加些少天拿水去開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔識嘅話都係搵師傅做啦</blockquote><br />\n過隔離重開先"},{"pid":"6f4a9a28974a2e2ed8433f74eafa2c9e550878f9","tid":56331,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6636ee46d1a79020932dfb61a3f3a977a074fc","tid":56331,"uid":60643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"剷哂上光油，批灰，再上乳膠漆"}]}